\par \pard\plain \ltrpar\s1{\*\hyphen2\hyphlead2\hyphtrail2\hyphmax0}\ql\rtlch\af0\afs24\lang1025\ltrch\dbch\af0\langfe255\hich\fs24\lang2057\loch\fs24\lang2057{\rtlch \ltrch\loch\f0\fs24\lang2057\i0\b0\rtlch\ltrch\dbch\hich\f2\fs22\loch\f2\fs22 [95]\tab We have found against the intervener both on the allegations relating to bundling and those related to foreclosure.  This, in itself, is of course not grounds for arguing that the intervention should not have been made.  The bundling issue was examine
